{"id":2892,"date":"2025-06-05T09:37:58","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T02:37:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2892"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:18:20","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:18:20","slug":"hoat-chat-cap-am","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/","title":{"rendered":"Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m &#8211; &#8220;Ch\u00eca kho\u00e1&#8221; cho l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng m\u1ecdng, kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1c <strong>ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m<\/strong> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0ng trong c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5-hoat-chat-am-cho-da-tot-nhat-2025\"><\/span><b>5+ Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u1ea9m cho da t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t 2025<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1c <strong>ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m<\/strong> s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 then ch\u1ed1t trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n &#8220;v\u00e0ng&#8221; gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hyaluronic-acid-ha-%e2%80%93-hoat-chat-hut-am-uu-viet\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid (HA) &#8211; Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1ea9m \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u01b0u gi\u1eef l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn 1.000 l\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh n\u00f3. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t &#8220;mi\u1ebfng b\u1ecdt bi\u1ec3n&#8221; t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n trong da, gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec cho b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2898\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2898\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/hoat-chat-ha\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2898\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2898\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-HA.webp\" alt=\"Hyaluronic Acid (HA) - Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1ea9m \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-HA.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-HA-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-HA-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-HA-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2898\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Hyaluronic Acid (HA) &#8211; Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1ea9m \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Hyaluronic Acid l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e1c r\u00e3nh n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1ecf, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t, s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><b> c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da kh\u00f4 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">v\u00e0 da thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"propylene-glycol\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Propylene Glycol<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Propylene Glycol l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Glycerin nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eddn r\u00edt. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u00fat \u1ea9m, gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t b\u00e1m d\u1eabn, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o da. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh d\u1ec5 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Propylene Glycol kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, gi\u00fap s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, Propylene Glycol c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"beta-glucan\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Beta-Glucan<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Beta-Glucan l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb n\u1ea5m men, y\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt kh\u00e1c, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da. Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2895\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2895\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2895\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2895\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc.webp\" alt=\"Beta-Glucan\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2895\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Beta-Glucan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Beta-Glucan c\u00f2n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n sinh collagen t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, Beta-Glucan c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"urea\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Urea<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong c\u00e1c <\/span><b>ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">th\u00ec, Urea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (NMF) c\u1ee7a da. Urea \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu cho da. Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat \u1ea9m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, Urea gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u1edbi. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, Urea c\u00f2n nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"squalane\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Squalane<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y gi\u00fap kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u1eddn r\u00edt hay b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, Squalane c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Squalane ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n, nh\u1edd k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u nh\u1eb9, th\u1ea5m nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2893\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2893\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2893\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2893\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da.webp\" alt=\"Squalane\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-cho-da-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2893\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Squalane<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hoat-chat-cap-am-glycerin\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m Glycerin<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycerin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, glycerin c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"aloe-vera-nha-dam\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Aloe Vera (Nha \u0111am)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nha \u0111am ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ebfn 99% n\u01b0\u1edbc, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i enzym, vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh l\u00e0m m\u00e1t, nha \u0111am c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, xoa d\u1ecbu v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a da. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, nha \u0111am c\u00f2n gi\u00fap da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2896\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2896\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2896\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2896\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat.webp\" alt=\"Aloe Vera (Nha \u0111am)\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-tot-nhat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2896\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Aloe Vera (Nha \u0111am)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hoat-chat-cap-am-sodium-pca\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m Sodium PCA<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sodium PCA l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (NMF) c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n trong da. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat \u1ea9m m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, Sodium PCA gi\u00fap da duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd li\u1ec1n, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t li\u00ean k\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sodium PCA \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho da kh\u00f4, thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 c\u0103ng m\u1ecdng d\u00e0i l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vitamin-e\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin E<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin E l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vitamin E c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, mang \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung vitamin E v\u00e0o chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb trung.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ceramide\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2894\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2894\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/hoat-chat-cap-am\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2894\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2894\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da.webp\" alt=\"Ceramide\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/hoat-chat-cap-am-da-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2894\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ceramide<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 then ch\u1ed1t trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng lipid, gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi da thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t ceramide, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung ceramide th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"panthenol\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Panthenol<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Panthenol (Provitamin B5) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da. Panthenol, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat \u1ea9m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4, c\u0103ng v\u00e0 bong tr\u00f3c, mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o. Nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh n\u00e0y, Panthenol \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. C\u00e1c <strong>ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m<\/strong> nh\u01b0 glycerin, nha \u0111am, sodium PCA, vitamin E, ceramide v\u00e0 panthenol kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh b\u00ean trong, r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o chu tr\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0ng trong c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2897,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[12],"class_list":["post-2892","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2892","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2892"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2892\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3970,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2892\/revisions\/3970"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2897"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2892"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2892"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2892"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}